  "texts": [
    "Knowledge-Grounded Dialogue (KGD) We report the performance of the models on the unseen test set (i.e.",
    "the knowledge base contains documents that are only present in the test set).",
    "The results show that models adapted using fine-tuning obtain a higher F1 than in-context learning.",
    "Furthermore, the best models tend to copy more from the gold knowledge compared to the annotators (as shown in the ground truth).",
    "Task-Oriented Dialogue (TOD) Differently from the other types, Llama2 C and Mistral I have obtained the best performance in terms of BLEU-4 when fine-tuned with no additional knowledge."
  ],
